Class InMemoryEventBroker

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.amcp.messaging.impl.InMemoryEventBroker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventBroker

    public class InMemoryEventBroker
extends Object
implements EventBroker
    Simple in-memory implementation of EventBroker for AMCP v1.5. Provides basic pub/sub functionality with topic pattern matching.
    Since:
    AMCP 1.5.0
